com.software.reuze

Class aa_SearchProblemNondeterministic

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.software.reuze.aa_SearchProblemNondeterministic

  • public class aa_SearchProblemNondeterministic
extends Object
    Non-deterministic problems may have multiple results for a given state and action; this class handles these results by mimicking Problem and replacing ResultFunction (one result) with aa_i_ResultsFunction (a set of results).
    Author:
    Andrew Brown
